description.en:
Green World is a community driven project that aims to work for a good and green ecosystem for earth.

We are planning to participate in lots of charity projects and are working for green world. For a better future, we want to support the recovery of the ecosystem, such as greening the world and avoiding pollution. 

Together with these, we will strive for living things to live a better life. we have goals such as opening water wells in places where there is no access to water in Africa. Everything is for Green World.
